  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CompoundForecast
    Wraps Forecast to provide a model that contains multiple Forecast objects.
    Forecast
    The main weather model.
    ForecastTemperature
    This model holds multiple Temperatures to represent a high/current/low structure.
    GeoCoordinate
    Represents a 2-dimension coordinate for the world.
    Location
    This model represents the location on the globe.
    MarsForecast
    A MarsForecast represents all the weather information on Mars as described in the project specifications.
    Pressure
    This model represents a pressure value, with its unit.
    SkyCondition
    This model represents the condition of the sky
    Speed
    This model represents the speed measure, with its unit
    Temperature
    This model represents the temperature measure, with its unit
    Velocity
    This model holds the velocity measure as a Speed and its unit
    WeatherData
    This model represents an aggregated weather model, to store all of the data acquired during a single refresh event.
